title: Welcome to Las Vegas
author: Unknown
pages:
The Welcome to Las
Vegas sign (In this
case the Welcome to
New Las Vegas Sign)
was built and installed
at the southern point
of the Las Vegas
Strip in 1959 by
Western Electric
under contract with
Clark County (The
county in which the
entire Las Vegas
metro area lies)...

Since the sign's design
was never
copyrighted and thus
its iconic design has is
used in countless
locations throughout
the Las Vegas valley.
